        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/power-paragon/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This raid build focuses on utilizing Warrior&#x27;s strong Dual Wielding trait on Paragon, allowing for a selfless low intensity DPS that&#x27;s great for group content.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It requires the Weaponmaster Training from Secrets of the Obscure to be able to wield the dagger as Paragon.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It also has high burst APM, as there is a 5 button combo that you ideally press quickly. Expect lower DPS if you do not press this combo quickly.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Consider it a more selfless alternative to the &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;aw2.help&#x2F;builds&#x2F;power-spellbreaker&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Magebane Daggerbreaker&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; build.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
