&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation&quot;&gt;Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the start of the fight, use all of the signets you have, saving &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;14410&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Fury for right when you are about to attack the boss.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;45252&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Breaching Strike (Dagger F1)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;14410&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Fury (won&#x27;t be available in opener)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77342&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chant of Action (F2) (only if it is not active or your motivation is less than 7)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;14518&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Crushing Blow (Mace 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;14415&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Tremor (Mace 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;14518&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Crushing Blow (Mace 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto until F1 is up again&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;45252&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Breaching Strike (Dagger F1)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;44937&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Disrupting Stab (Dagger 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto until Mace 5 has less than 2 seconds left on its cooldown&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes-1&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;relic&quot;&gt;Relic&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Upkeep Relic of the Claw with &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;14415&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Tremor (Mace 5) and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;44937&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Disrupting Stab (Dagger 3). The rotation is made in such a way that you are reaching ~90% uptime of Claw without much thought. For slightly higher Claw uptime, delay your Dagger 3 a little bit instead of doing it immediately after your Dagger F1.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can also use Relic of the Eagle for a DPS loss of ~3k.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;weapon-set-2-options&quot;&gt;Weapon Set 2 options&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;dagger-axe-for-more-dps-but-higher-apm&quot;&gt;Dagger &#x2F; Axe for more DPS but higher APM&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
