&lt;&#x2F;tbody&gt;&lt;&#x2F;table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remember you don&#x27;t need to buy a second Dagger; just equip the Axe offhand.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;spear-for-cc&quot;&gt;Spear for CC&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you need to do big CC, swap to Spear and use skills 3 and 5. Swap back once CC is done.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th&gt;Weapon&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Type&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Stat&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;th&gt;Upgrade&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;&lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;&lt;&#x2F;thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
	&lt;td&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot;
		data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot;
